Questiom stands hor Question Mesh

Questiom is:

  • a Web Application to answer questionnaires

  • a Desktop Application to build questionnaires

The questions are linked together in a huge mesh that extends to all knowledge areas.

Anyone can use Questiom
To download the PDF version of your questionnaire click the Download link.
To answer your questionnaire click the Answer button. Your answers won't be submitted until you click the Submit Button, at th end of the quesitonnaire.
